snippet.title: UNDEREVENT 2021: Undertale: The Otherground Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
thanks so much to you all for a good show :^)
we were so excited to have been a part of this, and are pleasantly surprised it was so well received! we unfortunately ran short on time, so we had to compromise a lot of ideas we had, so apologies for that

again, thanks for a wonderful UE21! we hope to see you again in UE22
and special thanks to Purrsum for helping us build this teaser!

links will be provided below:
undertale: the otherground gamejolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/UT_Otherground_Game_poody-Harper/255490
